law.text: All departments, divisions, boards, bureaus, commissions, or agencies of state government shall provide the commission data necessary to carry out its duties under KRS 163.510 and 163.515.
law.history: Amended 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 68, sec. 2, effective July 13, 1990. -- Created 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 160, sec. 5, effective July 15, 1982.
